    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really great shape, both inside and out. It runs super smoothly and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming adventures. Whether you\u2019re commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive. Can't wait to hear from you!",
