    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a reliable ride that still looks and feels great on the road. It runs super smoothly and I\u2019ve taken great care of it\u2014I\u2019m honestly going to miss it! Feel free to reach out if you have questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
